    This program tests the org.apache.derby.iapi.store.access.DiskHashtable class. The unit test interface is not used because that is undocumented and very difficult to decipher. Furthermore it is difficult to diagnose problems when using the unit test interface. Created: Wed Feb 09 15:44:12 2005
